example.solution:
\begin{aligned}
\text{Enter } &= \texttt{SUM(A1:A5)} \text{ in a cell.} \\
&= 100 + 200 + 150 + 300 + 250 \\
&= \boxed{1000}
\end{aligned}

\begin{aligned}
\text{Enter } &= \texttt{VLOOKUP("P003", A2:B5, 2, FALSE)} \text{ in a cell.} \\
\text{Looks up 'P003' in } A2:A5, \text{ returns value from column } 2. \\
&= \boxed{30}
\end{aligned}
